♪ I'M ALWAYS HERE.

02:10.782 --> 02:12.958
[HISSING]

02:15.700 --> 02:18.138
[OMINOUS MUSIC]

03:13.802 --> 03:14.672
-FORGET IT, MAN!

03:14.803 --> 03:16.065
I'M NOT GOING IN THERE,

03:16.196 --> 03:17.762
THIS PLACE
GIVES ME THE CREEPS.

03:17.893 --> 03:19.851
-THEN YOU CAN JUST FORGET
ABOUT BEING IN THE CLUB.

03:21.244 --> 03:22.637
-COME ON, CLIFFORD,

03:22.767 --> 03:24.378
WE ALL HAD TO GO THROUGH
THE SAME INITIATION.

03:25.205 --> 03:26.641
BUT IF YOU DON'T WANNA
BE IN THE CLUB...

03:26.771 --> 03:29.034
-NO, NO.
I WANNA BE IN THE CLUB.

03:34.431 --> 03:35.258
I'LL DO IT.

03:35.389 --> 03:36.477
-THAT'S BETTER.

03:36.607 --> 03:38.609
AROUND
THE LAST PYLON AND BACK.

03:38.740 --> 03:40.742
THEN YOU'LL OFFICIALLY
BE ONE OF US.

04:40.845 --> 04:41.933
-HELP!

04:43.544 --> 04:45.067
HELP!

04:46.242 --> 04:47.809
RICKY! HELP!

04:50.464 --> 04:52.901
HELP! HELP!

04:53.031 --> 04:55.469
PLEASE, SOMEONE! HELP!

04:58.036 --> 04:59.211
-WHAT'S THAT?

04:59.342 --> 05:00.517
-CLIFFORD:
COME ON, I NEED HELP!

05:03.564 --> 05:04.739
HELP!

05:14.705 --> 05:15.967
-WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO?

05:16.098 --> 05:17.012
HE'LL KILL HIM,
WE GOTTA GO FOR HELP!

05:17.142 --> 05:18.448
-YOU GO! HURRY!

05:42.951 --> 05:44.344
-BILLY!

05:44.474 --> 05:45.736
THERE'S A MONSTER
AND HE'S AFTER CLIFFORD!

05:45.867 --> 05:47.172
COME ON!

05:47.303 --> 05:48.609
-WHAT?
-COME ON, THERE'S A MONSTER!

05:52.352 --> 05:54.702
[COUGHING]

05:57.574 --> 05:59.489
[PANTING]

06:06.496 --> 06:07.889
[SCREAMING]

06:17.942 --> 06:19.509
-ARE YOU OK?

06:28.388 --> 06:29.693
-HE WAS HUGE!

06:29.824 --> 06:31.434
-HE WAS HIDEOUS!

06:31.565 --> 06:33.001
HIS HANDS WERE LIKE,
HAD THESE GLOVES ON THAT WERE,

06:33.131 --> 06:34.655
LIKE WRAPPED IN GAUZE.

06:35.220 --> 06:37.005
-HE HAD SOME KIND OF MASK ON.

06:37.135 --> 06:39.137
-HE WAS THE UGLIEST
THING I'VE EVER SEEN.

06:39.660 --> 06:42.576
-WHOEVER OR WHATEVER
HE WAS SURE SCARED HIM.

06:42.706 --> 06:44.273
I'VE NEVER SEEN MY
LITTLE BRO SO FRIGHTENED.

06:44.404 --> 06:45.796
-DID HE SAY ANYTHING?

06:46.493 --> 06:47.494
-NO.

06:47.624 --> 06:49.104
-HE JUST CAME OUT OF NOWHERE,

06:49.234 --> 06:50.671
THEN JUST DISAPPEARED AGAIN.

06:50.801 --> 06:52.194
-WELL, THE IMPORTANT THING
IS THAT YOU GUYS ARE OK.

06:52.847 --> 06:56.198
-AND NO MORE CLUB INITIATIONS
UNDER THE PIER, ALL RIGHT?

06:57.155 --> 06:58.853
-THANKS FOR BRINGING
'EM DOWN, BILLY.

06:59.549 --> 07:01.769
-I DIDN'T KNOW WHAT ELSE TO DO.
-NO, YOU DID THE RIGHT THING.

07:02.813 --> 07:04.815
-COME ON, GUYS.
-ALL RIGHT, SEE YA.

07:09.907 --> 07:13.084
-WHOEVER HE WAS,
HE SAVED MY LIFE.

07:14.564 --> 07:16.044
I WISH
I COULD'VE THANKED HIM.

07:16.174 --> 07:18.350
-I'D LIKE TO THANK
HIM FOR YOU, CLIFFORD.

07:19.830 --> 07:20.657
SEE YA.

07:22.659 --> 07:23.965
-YOU CAN GET TO YOUR
CAR JUST OVER THERE.

07:24.095 --> 07:25.009
-BILLY: OK, THANKS.

07:25.140 --> 07:26.097
-BYE.
-RICKY: BYE.

07:26.228 --> 07:27.098
-BYE.
-SEE YOU GUYS.

07:27.838 --> 07:29.449
BYE, CLIFFORD.
-CLIFFORD: BYE.

07:31.538 --> 07:32.930
-THEY COULDN'T
BE MAKING THAT UP.

07:33.061 --> 07:34.671
-NO, NO, I THINK THEY'RE
TELLING THE TRUTH.

07:34.802 --> 07:36.238
-SO WHO DO YOU THINK
THIS CREATURE IS?

07:36.368 --> 07:37.587
-I HAVEN'T THE SLIGHTEST.

07:38.283 --> 07:41.504
MAYBE WE HAVE OURSELVES
A PHANTOM LIFEGUARD.

08:00.131 --> 08:01.742
-HEY, YOU GUYS STILL
ON FOR DINNER TONIGHT?

08:02.569 --> 08:04.266
-OH, SURE, CODY WOULD
NEVER MISS A FREE MEAL.

08:04.396 --> 08:06.268
-WELL, THEN STOP PIGGING
OUT ON THE CHIPS.

08:06.398 --> 08:08.792
WE'RE HAVING LASAGNA
AND I WANT BIG APPETITES.

08:10.141 --> 08:12.666
-GO EASY ON THOSE,
THEY MAY BE MY ONLY
COMPANY THIS WEEKEND.

08:12.796 --> 08:14.319
-YOU OK?

08:14.450 --> 08:16.017
-CODY'S GOING ON ONE OF
THOSE JOCK GETAWAYS AGAIN.

08:16.931 --> 08:18.889
HE'S GONNA GO SURF THE WEDGE
AT NEWPORT THIS WEEKEND.

08:19.020 --> 08:20.891
-HMM, BIG STORM
COMING IN FROM MEXICO.

08:21.022 --> 08:22.023
HEAR THE SURF'S UP.

08:23.677 --> 08:25.243
AND I'M GUESSING
YOU'RE A LITTLE DOWN.

08:26.201 --> 08:27.419
-IF HE'S NOT PADDLING
WITH THE GUYS,

08:27.550 --> 08:28.551
HE MOUNTAIN BIKING
WITH THE GUYS.

08:29.596 --> 08:31.293
-WELL, DOES HE EVER
ASK YOU TO GO ALONG?

08:31.423 --> 08:33.034
-YEAH, BUT I JUST WANT TO
SPEND TIME WITH HIM, YOU KNOW?

08:33.164 --> 08:34.731
-HMM, ABSOLUTELY.

08:35.775 --> 08:38.429
THAT'S WHY I AM KIDNAPPING
MITCH THIS WEEKEND.

08:38.561 --> 08:39.693
-REALLY? WHERE
ARE YOU TAKING HIM?

08:39.823 --> 08:40.650
-I DON'T KNOW IF
YOU CAN HANDLE IT,

08:40.780 --> 08:41.650
IT'S PRETTY ROMANTIC.

08:42.390 --> 08:43.479
-GO AHEAD, I CAN HANDLE IT.

08:44.567 --> 08:47.091
-WE ARE DRIVING UP
THE COAST TO CARMEL,

08:47.222 --> 08:49.572
STAYING IN THIS GREAT PLACE

08:49.703 --> 08:53.881
WITH PRIVATE HOT TUBS
THAT OVERLOOK THE OCEAN.

08:54.011 --> 08:57.406
JUST ONE NIGHT, BUT I PLAN
TO MAKE IT UNFORGETTABLE.

08:58.450 --> 09:00.278
HEY, MAYBE YOU CAN GET CODY TO
TAKE YOU THERE NEXT WEEKEND.

09:00.409 --> 09:01.410
[LAUGHING]

09:01.541 --> 09:03.064
-YEAH, RIGHT.

09:03.194 --> 09:04.587
ROLLERBLADING ON SATURDAY,
KAYAKING ON SUNDAY.

09:05.109 --> 09:07.547
GIVE THAT UP FOR SOMETHING
AS BORING AS ROMANCE?

09:08.460 --> 09:09.505
NOT GONNA HAPPEN.

09:10.854 --> 09:12.595
-OH, THESE ARE
BEAUTIFUL FLOWERS,

09:12.726 --> 09:14.205
WHERE'D YOU GET 'EM?

09:14.336 --> 09:15.772
-OH, CODY LEFT THEM AT
MY TOWER THIS MORNING.

09:15.903 --> 09:17.818
-MAYBE HE'S CHANGING HIS WAYS.

09:17.948 --> 09:18.906
-MAYBE.
[KNOCKING]

09:19.036 --> 09:19.994
-COME IN!

09:22.126 --> 09:23.693
-HI, LADIES.
-HI.

09:23.824 --> 09:24.825
-HEY, I'VE BEEN LOOKING
ALL OVER FOR YOU.

09:24.955 --> 09:26.391
-REALLY?

09:26.522 --> 09:27.784
-YEAH, UH, HAVE YOU
SEEN MY ROLLERBLADES?

09:27.915 --> 09:30.178
-CODY, I THINK YOU
PICKED THE PERFECT TIME

09:30.308 --> 09:31.353
TO SURPRISE C.J.

09:31.483 --> 09:33.877
-OH, YEAH? HOW'S THAT?

09:34.791 --> 09:36.401
-WELL, I DON'T THINK
THAT SHE EXPECTED

09:36.532 --> 09:37.751
TO GET FLOWERS FROM YOU.

09:38.534 --> 09:39.709
-SHE DIDN'T.

09:39.840 --> 09:40.797
BUT YOU KNOW
I LOVE YOU, BABE.

09:41.581 --> 09:42.582
-DON'T CALL ME BABE.

09:46.586 --> 09:48.370
-WELL, IF THEY'RE NOT FROM
CODY, WHO ARE THEY FROM?

09:50.328 --> 09:51.286
-I DON'T KNOW.

09:58.293 --> 09:59.424
-RIGHT AROUND HERE.

09:59.555 --> 10:00.817
I DIDN'T SEE THE THING,

10:00.948 --> 10:02.079
MY LITTLE BRO AND
HIS BUDDIES DID.

10:02.776 --> 10:03.603
-SO WHERE IS HE?

10:04.255 --> 10:05.082
IT.

10:05.605 --> 10:07.476
-OH, DON'T WORRY,
HE'LL SHOW.

10:07.607 --> 10:09.739
WHEN HE DOES, WE'RE GONNA MAKE
BIG BUCKS OFF THIS UGLY DUDE.

10:12.612 --> 10:14.222
FRONT PAGE
OF THE ENQUIRER, MAN!

10:14.352 --> 10:15.484
HARD COPY!

10:16.267 --> 10:17.921
-SO LET ME GET THIS STRAIGHT.

10:18.052 --> 10:19.531
YOU WANT ME TO JUST HAND
AROUND HERE WITH MY CAMERA?

10:19.662 --> 10:21.011
BILLY, WHAT IF THIS GUY
DOESN'T SHOW UP FOR HOURS?

10:21.142 --> 10:22.360
OR DAYS?

10:22.491 --> 10:23.927
IF HE EVEN SHOWS UP AT ALL?

10:24.058 --> 10:25.189
-I'M NOT LAME, BRETT.

10:25.712 --> 10:27.365
CAN YOU JUST HOOK UP
A REMOTE CONTROL CAMERA?

10:27.496 --> 10:29.498
-WELL, YEAH, MY DAD OWNS
A SURVEILLANCE COMPANY.

10:30.194 --> 10:31.718
-EXCELLENT.

10:31.848 --> 10:32.849
WHY DON'T YOU GO GET
SOME LONG PLAY TAPES,

10:32.980 --> 10:34.242
GO HOME, COME BACK,

10:34.372 --> 10:35.504
CHECK OUT WHAT IT TAPES.

10:36.679 --> 10:37.811
PHANTOM OF THE PIER.

10:38.333 --> 10:40.074
THIS IS BETTER THAN
GETTING VIDEO OF BIGFOOT.

10:41.902 --> 10:42.816
COME ON, LET'S DO IT.

10:42.946 --> 10:44.034
-OK.

11:09.886 --> 11:14.412
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

11:45.313 --> 11:47.707
-UNBELIEVABLE!
IT'S GREAT, IT REALLY IS.

11:48.490 --> 11:50.013
-THANK YOU.
-HEY, BIG SWELL COMING THROUGH.

11:50.144 --> 11:50.927
THE SURF
IS SUPPOSED TO BE AWESOME.

11:51.058 --> 11:51.972
-I HEARD!

11:52.102 --> 11:53.713
-AWESOME MEANS DANGEROUS.

11:53.843 --> 11:55.323
-I WISH YOU WERE
COMING WITH US, BUDDY.

11:55.453 --> 11:56.933
-WELL, I'VE GOT
SOME AWESOME PLANS

11:57.064 --> 11:58.674
LINED UP
FOR MITCH THIS WEEKEND.

11:58.805 --> 12:01.198
-DOES AWESOME MEAN DANGEROUS?
-ONLY IF YOU RESIST.

12:06.247 --> 12:07.378
[SIGHING]

12:09.032 --> 12:10.338
-SO WHAT'S UP, KID?

12:10.468 --> 12:11.731
LOOKS LIKE YOU HAD
A ROUGH DAY, HUH?

12:12.340 --> 12:13.558
-NO, JUST WEIRD.

12:14.081 --> 12:15.560
-WHAT DO YOU MEAN, "WEIRD"?

12:15.691 --> 12:17.693
-SOMEONE LEFT C.J.
FLOWERS AT HER TOWER TODAY

12:17.824 --> 12:19.564
AND SHE'S A LITTLE
TICKED IT WASN'T ME.

12:19.695 --> 12:20.652
[LAUGHING]

12:21.523 --> 12:23.481
-FLOWERS AND A POEM.
-A POEM!

12:23.612 --> 12:24.787
SOUNDS ROMANTIC.

12:24.918 --> 12:26.484
-IT'S NOT ABOUT ROMANCE.

12:26.615 --> 12:28.704
GUY ARE ALWAYS LEAVING
GIFTS AT C.J.'S TOWER.

12:28.835 --> 12:29.879
-WELL, GIRLS LEAVE
THINGS FOR YOU.

12:30.010 --> 12:31.185
-YEAH, BUT I DON'T KEEP THEM.

12:31.315 --> 12:32.839
-SO WHAT'D THE POEM SAY?

12:33.753 --> 12:34.623
-I HAVE IT RIGHT HERE.

12:42.239 --> 12:45.242
"IT WAS MANY
AND MANY A YEAR AGO,
IN A KINGDOM BY THE SEA,

12:45.373 --> 12:47.505
"THAT A MAIDEN THERE
LIVED WHOM YOU MAY KNOW

12:47.636 --> 12:49.072
"BY THE NAME OF ANNABEL LEE.

12:49.899 --> 12:51.771
"AND THIS MAIDEN SHE LIVED
WITH NO OTHER THOUGHT

12:51.901 --> 12:54.077
THAN TO LOVE
AND BE LOVED BY ME."

12:54.861 --> 12:56.297
-MITCH: EDGAR ALLEN POE.

12:56.427 --> 12:57.515
-I WOULD LIKE TO KNOW
WHO THIS MYSTERY MAN IS.

12:57.646 --> 12:58.516
-ME, TOO.

12:59.169 --> 13:00.431
HE'S CERTAINLY ROMANTIC.

13:00.562 --> 13:01.781
-OR A NUTCASE.

13:01.911 --> 13:03.608
-WELL, WHOEVER IT IS,

13:03.739 --> 13:05.393
IT SOUNDS LIKE YOU GOT A LITTLE
COMPETITION THERE, COOKIE.

13:06.046 --> 13:08.048
-YEAH, IT SOUNDS LIKE
C.J.'S GOT HERSELF

13:08.178 --> 13:09.179
A SECRET ADMIRER.

13:23.019 --> 13:24.107
-BILLY: IS THERE ENOUGH LIGHT?

13:24.238 --> 13:25.848
-THIS IS MADE FOR SURVEILLANCE.

13:25.979 --> 13:27.241
IT'S INFRARED SENSITIVE.

13:32.376 --> 13:34.944
-THIS IS GONNA BE GREAT, DUDE!
-I DON'T KNOW, BILLY.

13:35.075 --> 13:38.252
THIS IS WEIRD. I MEAN,
WE'RE TRACKING MONSTERS HERE.

13:39.209 --> 13:40.689
-HEY, MONSTERS THAT MEAN MONEY.

13:40.820 --> 13:42.212
BIG MONEY.

13:43.561 --> 13:44.432
IS IT READY?

13:46.042 --> 13:47.348
-YEAH, IT'S READY.

13:47.478 --> 13:48.479
-WELL, TURN IT ON.

13:51.569 --> 13:52.788
-LET'S GET THE LADDER.

13:57.097 --> 13:58.141
COME ON.
-LET'S GO.

14:04.452 --> 14:06.497
[UPBEAT MUSIC]

14:21.817 --> 14:24.211
♪ I DON'T NEED ANYTHING

14:24.341 --> 14:27.823
♪ EXCEPT WHAT I HAVE IN FRONT OF ME

14:28.519 --> 14:30.521
♪ I GIVE IT ALL I'VE GOT ♪

14:30.652 --> 14:33.742
